Que caraças.

238
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:46,555
Meu Deus.

239
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:49,790
Obrigada.

240
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:56,192
- Purdue Creamery.
- Morgan?

241
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:58,351
