252
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,720
Ligas-me depois?

253
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:25,510
Adeus.

254
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:33,834
Meu...

255
00:17:45,280 --> 00:17:46,475
Tu existes.

256
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:49,315
Pensava que tinha sonhado
na noite passada.

257
